6. Core Business Rules

BR-PUR-001

Every purchase requires identity information.

BR-PUR-002

Purchase amount must be calculated automatically.

BR-PUR-003

Approved purchases cannot be deleted.

BR-PUR-004

Inventory records created automatically after approval.

BR-PUR-005

Purchase ledger immutable after approval.

BR-PUR-006

Photos mandatory for scrap purchases.

BR-PUR-007

Weight and purity required.

BR-PUR-008

Audit log mandatory for all approvals.

