8. Valuation Engine

Purpose

Calculate purchase amount.

⸻

Net Weight Formula

Net\ Weight = Gross\ Weight - Stone\ Weight

⸻

Fine Weight Formula

Fine\ Weight = Net\ Weight \times Purity\ Factor

⸻

Purchase Amount Formula

Purchase\ Amount = Fine\ Weight \times Market\ Rate

